<h3>サンプル</h3>

sin,cos,tanを求めるサンプルです。

<pre>
use strict;
use warnings;
use Math::Trig qw/tan pi/;

# sin(90°) = 1;
print "sin(π/2) = " . sin(pi/2) . "\n";

# cos(60°) = 1/2;
print "cos(π/3) = " . cos(pi/3) . "\n";

# tan(45°) = 1;
print "tan(π/4) = " . tan(pi/4) . "\n";
</pre>
